body: I built TensorFlow from source (last update: yesterday) with CUDA 8.0 and cuDNN 5.1 on Ubuntu 16.04.2, downloaded the Inference Library from [nightly-android#79](https://ci.tensorflow.org/view/Nightly/job/nightly-android/79/) and running the inference on a Nexus 6P as host device.
